{"type": "article", "id": 36179, "title": "BAPE发布新年福袋，以及，这里有一份日式风格着装示范 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-29T02:48:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3659, "name": "Oscar de la Renta"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 35088, "name": "蔦屋书店"}, {"id": 36295, "name": "日式风格"}, {"id": 36297, "name": "日本零售业"}, {"id": 7422, "name": "Nasty Gal"}, {"id": 36298, "name": "Boohoo"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161229100524yM3QpOrgz7t5m1PZ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/dec/28/boohoo-set-to-bid-for-us-fashion-label-nasty-gal\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国时尚电商 Boohoo 加入对美国电商 Nasty Gal 的品牌竞标</b></a> | 曾经红极一时的美国电商 Nasty Gal 在上个月申请破产保护，诞生于曼彻斯特的 Boohoo 宣布计划斥资 2000 万美元收购 Nasty Gal。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.investing.com/news/economic-indicators/japan-rsquo;s-retail-sales-1.7-vs.-0.9-forecast-450089\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>十一月，日本的零售业增幅高于预期</b></a> | 日本的零售业似乎有复苏的迹象。据日本经济贸易产业省发布的数据表明，在十一月，日本全国的零售业增长了 1.7%，相比之下，十月的零售业增幅为 0.1%。而分析师在上个月预测的 11 月增幅为 0.9%，大大高于预期。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/29/vetements-staff-ss17/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements  又出了新的套头衫</a>，这次是以 Staff 为主题的。该主题系列包括一个短袖 T 和一个白色连帽衫，在 colette 网店上的售价分别为 296 和 506 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100906zC8OfS2FPnrAjqLY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100906D4xkfPsOa5R02n8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100919Z07zltfdXajLxYUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100932ZVCLEnwKfMjspINk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/adidas-ultraboost-atr-mid-primeknit-first-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 推出 UltraBOOST 高筒鞋款 ATR Mid Primeknit</a>，它的鞋面采用与 UltraBOOST 3.0 相同之独特纹理细节，并搭载加厚外底，这双鞋将于 2017 年年初发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100944nA7uwMfsK1FtQlbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667467\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100944ldgRVqy4DkMvpiIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229100956sf4WorknA7iSpba3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/bape-2017-happy-new-year-bag\" rel=\"nofollow\">BAPE 推出 2017 新年福袋</a>。这次的福袋包括「A BATHING APE」、「BAPE」及「BABY MILO」三个版本，其中只有男装的「A BATHING APE」版本定价最贵，为 39800 日元。搭载 APE HEAD 图案背包的「BAPE」版，有男装、女装、童装三个版本，「BABY MILO」则分为男装和童装版，以 BABY MILO 图案的背包装载。这两款福袋的成人版为 19800 日元，童装版为 16800 日元，将于元旦在日本指定的 BAPE 店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101005teG6gpUXaKF42S1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612291010142zIc3kYHrMwasnLp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101014BjU7IdS80q1TeLkb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101015ceE81qmalhG6KSH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>设计师 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/oscar-de-la-renta-to-be-featured-on-u-s-postal-stamps-10734450/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oscar de la Renta 将在 2017 年被印在美国邮票上</a>，这套邮票共有 11 张，其中有 10 张是他本人的设计，还有一张是他的黑白肖像。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101042DjBCnxYKp5NcQGgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.128843\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来自洛杉矶的街头品牌<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/24/chinatown-market-reversible-bomber/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Chinatown Market 推出了新款夹克衫和连帽衫系列</a>。其经典的玫瑰花元素再次出现，售价 140 美元，也依然很平易近人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101055f5yCAp1ZscFVjQgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101103at7fMXT8V9psBRb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101110hCLAd82cE9o4yxMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101110mzeMIEfV78kBHX4F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101118OKxDTguZHBvqmLRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101118ku5Q8N0rDHLI34bR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/tsutaya-bookstore-taiwan-opening/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">蔦屋书店进驻台湾</a>，将于 1 月 24 在统一时代台北店的五楼开业。这家书店名为 TSUTAYA BOOKSTORE TAIWAN，除了引进大量的日文书籍、杂志外，还将引进日本涩谷的咖啡店 WIRED TOKYO。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101131XV74BgkrLoewhTPE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">波士顿潮流名店<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/28/bodega-layering-editorial/#slide-8\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Bodega 发布的最新造型特辑</a>，示范了“如何演绎日式风格”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101200e32CoVHW9t5jLsDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101200POJ4IaZMpYBfAmbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101200f1k2MRm0zPJhrduB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101201o4K5J3GZ8mhVRgyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101201DA8jt0rkPZgKhIiB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101201PqSe73KMwVzQRihB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161229101209sZWCpRVSjn1geD8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612291012093pMXmFAIY7OClGfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/28/bodega-layering-editorial/#slide-8\" rel=\"nofollow\">hisnobiety</a></p>"}